To run the simulation you have to provide just one parameter which is the name
of a data file.

    ./lbsim <name> <flag> <name of vtk file(For flow around object)>

following possible simulation flags has to be set up:
     -fcavity   :    For Lid Driven Cavity
     -fstep     :    Flow over step
     -fchannel  :    Pressure Driven shear flow in channel
     -fplate    :    Flow around Tilted Plate

EXAMPLE:
	in general: 
		./lbsim step.data -fstep
	
	for tilted plate:
		 ./lbsim plate.data -fplate lbm_tilted_plate.vtk

HINT: Check spelling of your data file if the simulation doesn't run
